description: Solnaberg Property AB engages in the developing and managing of real properties. The company is headquartered in Goeteborg, Vastra Gotalands. The company went IPO on 2016-10-12. The firm operates as a real estate manager and it owns property Solna Bladet 3. The firm's property is located in Bergshamra, in the east of Solna region. The firm leases its property to various tenants.
name: Solnaberg Property AB (publ)
